I hope I did you a favor in terms of form validation and that sort of thing,

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:05.000
so you can see how you do it the old fashioned way,

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.000
before you reach the AJAX.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:11.000
AJAX isn't always the right tool.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:14.000
But as I just kind of alluded tool, form validation--when you type in all those things--

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:17.000
just hitting submit and then getting your errors without reloading the whole page

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
is a really common use of Ajax.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.000
But you still need to validate things when you submit the form for real,

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:26.000
